      "clean_text": "One of the issues he considered was whether the AFP was entitled to immunity under s 14 of the SIA 1978 as falling within the expression ‘the government’ in s 14(1)(b) or a ‘department of that government’ (in s 14(1)(c)), both of which are entitled to the general immunity conferred by s 1(1) and to which the exceptions to immunity in the Act apply."
